```plantuml
@startuml zalando-incubator_fabric-gateway

actor User
participant "FabricGateway CRD" as CRD
participant "Gateway Operator" as Operator
participant "IngressDerivationChain" as IDC
participant "StackSetOperations" as SSO
participant "Kubernetes API" as K8S
participant "Skipper" as Skipper
participant "Backend Service" as Backend

User -> CRD: Creates/Updates FabricGateway resource
CRD -> Operator: Watches for changes
Operator -> IDC: Triggers derivation chain
IDC -> SSO: Requests service discovery
SSO -> K8S: Queries StackSet resources
K8S --> SSO: Returns service endpoints
SSO --> IDC: Provides service info
IDC -> IDC: Applies policies (auth, rate limiting)
IDC -> K8S: Generates Ingress resources
K8S -> Skipper: Updates routing configuration
User -> Skipper: API request
Skipper -> Backend: Proxies request (with policies enforced)
Backend --> Skipper: Returns response
Skipper --> User: Returns response

@enduml
```